<header class="page-hero"><div class="page-width--narrow"><span class="eyebrow">The Bible Band™</span><h1 class="display-title">Questions? We've Got Answers.</h1><p>Everything you need to know about NFC, compatibility, daily use, and what's inside every tap.</p></div></header>
<div class="page-width--narrow">
  <section class="faq-group"><div class="faq-group__head"><span class="faq-number">01</span><h2>What Is The Bible Band™?</h2></div>
    <details class="faq-item" open><summary>What is The Bible Band™?</summary><div class="rte"><p>The Bible Band™ is a Christian NFC wristband designed to help you keep God's Word close every day. One tap opens daily Scripture, a pastor-written devotion, guided prayer, audio, large-print text, and a free One-Year Bible Reading Plan—no app, login, or subscription required.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Who created The Bible Band™?</summary><div class="rte"><p>The Bible Band™ was created by Pastor Clark Whitney, a pastor in South Arkansas. Clark is a husband, dad, pastor, professor, and lifelong student of Scripture, with a Doctor of Education in Christian Leadership and ministry experience across Arkansas, Tennessee, and Georgia.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>What does The Bible Band™ include?</summary><div class="rte"><p>Every tap opens daily Scripture, a pastor-written devotion, guided prayer, audio, a large-print option, and a free One-Year Bible Reading Plan.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Why is it called The Bible Band™?</summary><div class="rte"><p>The name comes from Deuteronomy 11:18, where God tells His people to bind His words on their hands as a reminder to carry truth with them always. The Bible Band™ is a modern expression of that ancient practice.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Is the content written by AI?</summary><div class="rte"><p>No. Every devotion is written by a real pastor—not AI. The content is biblically faithful, theologically grounded, and written with genuine pastoral care.</p></div></details>
  </section>
  <section class="faq-group"><div class="faq-group__head"><span class="faq-number">02</span><h2>How Does NFC Work?</h2></div>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>What is NFC?</summary><div class="rte"><p>NFC stands for Near Field Communication—the same technology used for contactless payments. The Bible Band™ has a tiny NFC chip embedded inside it. Hold your phone close and it opens a web page in under a second.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Is NFC safe?</summary><div class="rte"><p>Yes. NFC is a widely used, well-established technology. The Bible Band™ chip only opens a webpage; it doesn't collect data, track your location, or access your phone.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Does The Bible Band™ have a battery?</summary><div class="rte"><p>No. The chip draws a tiny amount of energy from your phone's radio signal when you tap. It never needs charging or replacing.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>How long will the NFC chip last?</summary><div class="rte"><p>NFC chips are built to last for years of normal use, with no battery to die and no moving parts to break down.</p></div></details>
  </section>
  <section class="faq-group"><div class="faq-group__head"><span class="faq-number">03</span><h2>Compatibility</h2></div>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Does it work with iPhone?</summary><div class="rte"><p>Yes—iPhone 7 and newer. On iPhone XS and newer, NFC is active in the background. On iPhone 7 and 8, open Control Center and tap the NFC icon first. Hold the top edge of your phone near the chip.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Does it work with Android?</summary><div class="rte"><p>Yes—most Android phones made after 2018, including Samsung Galaxy, Google Pixel, OnePlus, and Motorola. Hold the center of the back of your phone near the chip.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Do I need an app?</summary><div class="rte"><p>No. Your phone opens a web page automatically—no App Store, download, login, or account required.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Does it require a subscription?</summary><div class="rte"><p>No. You pay once for The Bible Band™ and the daily content is free to access.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Does it need internet access?</summary><div class="rte"><p>The band itself needs no power source, but your phone needs Wi-Fi or cellular data to load the daily page after the tap.</p></div></details>
  </section>
  <section class="faq-group"><div class="faq-group__head"><span class="faq-number">04</span><h2>How To Use It</h2></div>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Walk me through it.</summary><div class="rte"><ol><li>Put on the band.</li><li>Unlock your phone.</li><li>Tap the top edge of an iPhone or center back of an Android near the chip.</li><li>Tap the notification banner.</li><li>Read, listen, and pray.</li></ol></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Can I listen instead of read?</summary><div class="rte"><p>Yes. Every daily devotion includes an audio version—great for mornings, commutes, walks, or quiet time.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>What is the One-Year Bible Reading Plan?</summary><div class="rte"><p>A free reading schedule included with every Bible Band™, walking you through the entire Bible over one year in short daily readings. No sign-up required.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Can I read a past devotion?</summary><div class="rte"><p>Yes. Previous devotions are accessible on the website, so you can catch up if you miss a day.</p></div></details>
  </section>
  <section class="faq-group"><div class="faq-group__head"><span class="faq-number">05</span><h2>Care &amp; Durability</h2></div>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Can I wear it in water?</summary><div class="rte"><p>The Bible Band™ is safe for typical daily activities and hand-washing. We recommend removing it before swimming, showering, or prolonged water exposure.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Can I sleep in it?</summary><div class="rte"><p>Yes. Many people wear their Bible Band™ around the clock as a constant reminder of God's presence.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>Will the NFC chip wear out?</summary><div class="rte"><p>NFC chips have no moving parts and no battery, so under normal conditions the chip should keep working reliably for the life of the band.</p></div></details>
  </section>
  <section class="faq-group"><div class="faq-group__head"><span class="faq-number">06</span><h2>Ordering &amp; Shipping</h2></div>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>How long does shipping take?</summary><div class="rte"><p>Standard shipping typically takes 3–7 business days within the United States. Expedited options may be available at checkout. International times vary.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>What is your return policy?</summary><div class="rte"><p>If your Bible Band™ arrives damaged or defective, contact us within 30 days of receiving your order and we'll work quickly to make it right.</p></div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary>I still have a question. Who do I contact?</summary><div class="rte"><p>Reach out through our <a href="/pages/contact">contact page</a> and Pastor Clark or a team member will get back to you personally.</p></div></details>
  </section>
</div>
